nginx/certs/

# Configurações locais do VS Code e instruções pessoais do Copilot
.vscode/settings.json
.github/instructions/personas/

# ============================================================
# AI / Agent Context Optimization (heavy agent usage)
# Files stay in git for humans/history but are excluded from
# agent context via .copilotignore / .claudeignore + editor settings
# ============================================================
docs/archive/
docs/*decommissioning*
docs/*audit*
docs/*remediation*
docs/*modernization*
docs/*continuation*
docs/*plan*.md
docs/*report*.md
docs/*coverage-plan*
docs/*strategy*.md
docs/*help*
*Grok*.md
*-help.md

# Large/noisy files agents rarely need full
frontend/package-lock.json

# Legacy and static content rarely edited by agents
legacy/
src/main/resources/static/layout/vendors/
